    <item>
      <title>英国在谈判中的南方水，以避免像泰晤士河一样的债务危机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/uk-s-southern-water-in-talks-to-avoid-thames-like-debt-crisis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国南部水公司（Southern Water Ltd.）正试图确定其财务状况，以保持其投资级别的地位，维护其资产负债表＆Mdash;并避免与泰晤士河水一样的债务困扰。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/uk-s-southern-water-in-talks-to-avoid-thames-like-debt-crisis</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Mar 2025 17:21:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>财政部在关税焦虑中恢复了一年的低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/treasury-yields-head-back-toward-year-s-lows-on-tariff-angst</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国政府债券收益率转移到了一年中最低水平，因为投资者坚信，贸易引起的增长放缓将导致美联储在2025年多次降低利率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/treasury-yields-head-back-toward-year-s-lows-on-tariff-angst</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Mar 2025 16:13:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>糖果制造商火星正在出售年度最大的美国债券，以资助Kellanova购买</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/mars-kicks-off-jumbo-dollar-bond-sale-to-fund-kellanova-takeover</link>
      <description><![CDATA[火星公司周三将出售260亿美元的美国高级债券，以资助其对竞争对手食品制造商Kellanova的收购，这是迄今为止年度最大的债券销售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/mars-kicks-off-jumbo-dollar-bond-sale-to-fund-kellanova-takeover</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Mar 2025 13:10:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Blackstone购买基础设施公司ITE的股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/blackstone-buys-stake-in-infrastructure-firm-ite-management</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Blackstone Inc.的信用和保险公司正在购买ITE Management＆Mdash;一家专注于投资运输基础设施＆Mdash的公司；一份声明说，并从中购买了多达20亿美元的投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/blackstone-buys-stake-in-infrastructure-firm-ite-management</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Mar 2025 12:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国的“一切都需要”的时刻为欧洲市场提供动力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/germany-s-whatever-it-takes-moment-powers-european-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国的历史性计划在周三增加支出震撼欧洲市场，为股票提供动力，超越美国同行，从与美元的平等边缘恢复了欧元，并将德国栏杆委托到自1990年以来最糟糕的一天。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/germany-s-whatever-it-takes-moment-powers-european-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Mar 2025 11:41:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着对美国增长的怀疑，新兴市场集会，关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/europe-leads-emerging-market-rally-as-us-dominance-is-challenged</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在赌注上获得的新兴资产较高的关税将减缓美国经济，并将投资流入其他市场，而交易员继续评估唐纳德·特朗普总统的征税是否会被退回。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/europe-leads-emerging-market-rally-as-us-dominance-is-challenged</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Mar 2025 10:50:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>自2015年球迷以来，欧元的最佳集会进一步增长了10％</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/traders-add-bets-on-euro-surging-10-more-as-parity-talk-dies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自2015年以来，欧元最佳的为期三天的集会鼓励交易者押注该货币在未来几个月内将进一步上涨10％。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/traders-add-bets-on-euro-surging-10-more-as-parity-talk-dies</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Mar 2025 10:28:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲燃气公牛的加深撤退会放大大价波动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/europe-gas-swings-as-traders-exit-market-on-mounting-uncertainty</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对欧洲天然气的看涨情绪正在急剧退缩，随着一些投资者在越来越多的地缘政治不确定性的情况下退出市场时，价格下波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/europe-gas-swings-as-traders-exit-market-on-mounting-uncertainty</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Mar 2025 08:21:58 GMT</pubDate>
